<% content_for :page_title, @public ? "What will happen after you report the teacher for serious misconduct" : "What will happen after you refer the teacher for serious misconduct" %>
<% content_for :back_link_url, @previous_path %>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds-from-desktop">
    <% if @public %>
        <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">
          What will happen after you report the teacher for serious misconduct
        </h1>

        <p class="govuk_body">
          The Teaching Regulation Agency (TRA) will usually contact you within 3 working days of receiving your report.
        </p>

        <p class="govuk_body">
          If they decide to investigate, your name and details of the report will be shared with the teacher and their employer. You may need to give evidence at a hearing.
        </p>

        <p class="govuk_body">
          It could take several months for the outcome to be decided. The TRA will tell you the outcome of their decision.
        </p>

        <p class="govuk_body">
          If your case is not investigated, your report may still be shared with the teacher. Your name and contact details will not be shared.
        </p>
  <% else %>
      <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">
        What will happen after you refer the teacher for serious misconduct
      </h1>

      <p class="govuk_body">
        The TRA will check your referral to see if it falls within the TRAâ€™s responsibilities.
      </p>

      <p class="govuk_body">
        To make this decision, they may require further information from you. They will write to you if they need this.
      </p>

      <p class="govuk_body">
        If your referral falls within their responsibilities, they will assess it to determine if an investigation is required.
      </p>

      <p class="govuk_body">
        If your referral is investigated, your name and allegation will be shared with the teacher and their employer. Your contact details will not be shared.
      </p>

      <p class="govuk_body">
        You might need to give evidence at a hearing.
      </p>

      <p class="govuk_body">
        Your referral may be kept on file for up to 50 years.
      </p>

  <% end %>

    <%= govuk_button_link_to "I understand and want to continue", @continue_path, classes: 'govuk-!-margin-top-2 govuk-!-margin-bottom-9' %>
  </div>
</div>
